                                        i.fas.fa-star
                                        i.fas.fa-star
                                        i.fas.fa-star
                                        i.fas.fa-star
                                        i.fas.fa-star
                                    span.reviewArthor Charlie Chaplin
                                    small.reviewTimestamp 12 August 2018
                                .col-12
                                    p It was okay.  Coffee wasn't great.
        .col-12.col-lg-3
            p.lead
                | Starcups is on Loc8r beacuse it has accessible wifi and space to sit down with you laptop and get some work done.
